---
description: shadcn UI and Zustand usage rules
globs:
  - "src/**/*.ts"
  - "src/**/*.tsx"
---

UI rules:
- Prefer shadcn/ui components for reusable app UI primitives
- Keep styling consistent with Tailwind utility classes already used in the codebase
- Prefer accessible patterns and semantic HTML
- Reuse existing UI primitives before creating new ones

Zustand rules:
- Use Zustand only for client-side UI/app state that does not belong on the server
- Good Zustand use cases:
  - sidebar state
  - dialog state
  - local board interaction state
  - ephemeral filters
  - optimistic UI state for rich interactions
- Do not use Zustand as a default data-fetching layer
- Do not duplicate server state in Zustand unless there is a clear UX reason

When state is server-owned:
- Prefer server rendering, URL params, Server Actions, or targeted client fetching patterns over global client stores